# TaskMaster 📝
A console-based Java to-do list manager that demonstrates full object-oriented programming principles Project #1.

## 📌 Features
- Create regular and priority tasks
- Set task descriptions and deadlines
- Sort tasks by deadline or priority level
- Search tasks by title
- Remove tasks from the list
- All data handled using an ArrayList

## 🧠 Concepts Demonstrated
- ✅ Inheritance: `PriorityTask` extends `Task`
- ✅ Encapsulation: Private fields + getters/setters
- ✅ Constructor Overloading
- ✅ Overriding: `toString()` and `equals()`
- ✅ Java Collections: `ArrayList<Task>`
- ✅ Interface: `Comparable` for sorting logic

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Java 17
- CLI (no GUI)
- VS Code / Terminal

## 🏁 How to Run

```bash
javac *.java
java App
